## Attribution

This project is an enhanced version of [Frontend Slides](https://github.com/zarazhangrui/frontend-slides)
by @zarazhangrui, licensed under the MIT License.

The following components are original contributions by Hongqing W:
- LAYOUT_PATTERNS.md — layout pattern library
- animation-patterns.md — entrance animation and chart animation system
- CDN accessibility fixes (cdnjs.cloudflare.com migration)
- Font Awesome icon rendering fixes
- Page entrance animation system (CSS pre-hide + JS reveal dual-track approach)
- ECharts chart animation presets (line/pie/bar/radar type-specific timing)
- Cover animation system (@keyframes + .cover-el pattern)
- Full-viewport background architecture (html-level gradient + fixed decorative elements)
- Cover animation JS trigger safeguard (forced reflow for reliable @keyframes replay)
- Theme CSS priority defense strategy (post-link style placement + !important fallbacks)
- Rank bar animation system (data-w attribute + forced reflow pattern)
- Content page readability overlay (semi-transparent gradient background on slides)
